## The 10 Experts (Quick Reference)

| Expert | Why They're Here |
|--------|-----------------|
| **Justin Welsh** | Built $2M+ solo business purely from LinkedIn. Proven content systems that generate inbound. |
| **Dave Gerhardt** | Ex-CMO at Drift ($1B valuation). Coined "founder brand." Runs Exit Five — 5,600+ B2B marketers. |
| **Chris Walker** | GTM advisor for SaaS $10M–$100M. Popularized dark social and demand gen framing. |
| **Lara Acosta** | One of LinkedIn's fastest-growing B2B creators. Post production systems at scale. |
| **Guillaume Moubeche** | CEO of lemlist. Built a $30M ARR SaaS brand almost entirely through founder-led LinkedIn content. |
| **Ross Simmonds** | CEO of Foundation. The go-to voice on B2B content distribution strategy. |
| **April Dunford** | Author of *Obviously Awesome*. Positioning expert — how to make LinkedIn content land with the right ICP. |
| **Amanda Natividad** | VP Marketing at SparkToro. Pioneered "zero-click content" — content designed to give value without requiring a click. |
| **Katelyn Bourgoin** | "Customer Whisperer." Buyer psychology → content that speaks directly to how B2B buyers make decisions. |
| **Devin Reed** | Former Head of Content at Gong. Built content systems that tied directly to revenue at one of SaaS's fastest-growing companies. |

Full annotations and links → [`/research/sources.md`](./research/sources.md)

