## How Content Was Collected

### LinkedIn Posts
Collected manually by visiting each expert's LinkedIn profile → Activity → Posts. Each post saved as a `.md` file with date, engagement metrics (where visible), and post type noted.

### YouTube Transcripts
Collected using `yt-dlp` — free, no API key required.

```bash
yt-dlp --write-auto-sub --skip-download --sub-lang en \
  --convert-subs srt \
  -o "%(uploader)s - %(title)s" \
  "VIDEO_URL"
```

### Other Materials
- Richard van der Blom's LinkedIn Algorithm Insights Report 2024/2025
- Exit Five newsletter issues (Dave Gerhardt)
- SparkToro research referenced by Amanda Natividad

